            Chorus:<br>
            Oh, in this rainy season, my heart aches,<br>
            Without you, the magic of the rain breaks,<br>
            Not just this season, but every time,<br>
            I want you here, forever mine.<br><br>

            Bridge:<br>
            From teenage dreams to twilight years,<br>
            Through joy and sorrow, laughter and tears,<br>
            I want to hold you, through it all,<br>
            Together, forever, we'll stand tall.<br><br>

            Chorus:<br>
            Oh, in this rainy season, my heart aches,<br>
            Without you, the magic of the rain breaks,<br>
            Not just this season, but every time,<br>
            I want you here, forever mine.<br><br>

            Verse 3:<br>
            The moon won’t shine, the night feels cold,<br>
            Without you, life seems so old,<br>
            God, why can't you hear my call?<br>
            Bring my love back, through it all.<br><br>

            Chorus:<br>
            Oh, in this rainy season, my heart aches,<br>
            Without you, the magic of the rain breaks,<br>
            Not just this season, but every time,<br>
            I want you here, forever mine.<br><br>

            Outro:<br>
            The rain keeps falling, but I feel no joy,<br>
            Until you're here, my love, my soul's decoy,<br>
